SAGAN: <i>Humason by now had</i>
<i>his own night assistant...</i>

15:11.140 --> 15:13.540
<i>... to help him with the observations.</i>

15:15.611 --> 15:18.546
HUMASON: Afternoon, Mr. Nelson.
